  "instructions": [
    "Cook the rice stick noodles according to the package instructions and set aside.",
    "In a large pan or wok, heat 1tbsp of vegetable oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the sliced onion and cook until translucent, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the beef strips and cook until browned, about 5-6 minutes.",
    "Add the fish sauce, lime juice, grated ginger, chili flakes, salt, and sugar. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the diced tomatoes and stir-fry for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add the cooked noodles and stir-fry for an additional 2-3 minutes.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve hot and garnish with fresh herbs, if desired."
